Killer CALANGO (Jogos Senac CAS (TJD e BJD)) is a platformer game developed by Jogos Senac CAS. It was originally released in 2021.
You can play Killer CALANGO (Jogos Senac CAS (TJD e BJD)) on PC. The game is sold via itch.io.
